## Structure

### File Organization
```
floating/
├── main.py              # Entry point
├── ball_window.py       # Main widget (BallWindow class)
├── settings_dialog.py   # Settings UI (SettingsDialog class)
├── auth_service.py      # OAuth login (AuthService class)
├── api_service.py       # API requests (APIService class)
├── themes/
│   ├── __init__.py      # Theme registry (THEMES dict)
│   ├── base_theme.py    # BaseTheme ABC, BallData class
│   ├── color_themes.py  # ColorTheme definitions
│   ├── space_theme.py   # Space theme (dual dials)
│   ├── glacier_theme.py # Glacier theme (water + ice)
│   └── ...              # Other themes
├── scripts/             # Development/test scripts
├── *.knowledge          # Design documentation
└── requirements.txt
```

### Data Flow
```
┌─────────────────┐      ┌──────────────┐      ┌─────────────────┐
│   AuthService   │ ──▶  │  APIService  │ ──▶  │   BallWindow    │
│  (OAuth/Cookies)│      │ (Usage Data) │      │ (Display/Theme) │
└─────────────────┘      └──────────────┘      └─────────────────┘
        ▲                                              │
        │                                              ▼
   Playwright                                    Theme.draw_ball()
   (Browser Login)                                     │
                                                       ▼
                                                  QPainter
```

### Key Classes
| Class | File | Responsibility |
|-------|------|----------------|
| `BallWindow` | ball_window.py | Main widget, animation, context menu |
| `SettingsDialog` | settings_dialog.py | Settings UI, theme selection |
| `AuthService` | auth_service.py | Login, cookies, org selection |
| `APIService` | api_service.py | Fetch usage data, organizations |
| `BaseTheme` | themes/base_theme.py | Theme interface (abstract) |
| `BallData` | themes/base_theme.py | Data container for ball rendering |

### Storage Locations
| Data | Location |
|------|----------|
| Cookies | `~/.floating-ball/cookies.json` |
| Config | `~/.floating-ball/config.json` |
| Settings | `~/Library/Preferences/FloatingBall/ClaudeUsage.plist` |

## Tools

### Running the App
```bash
# Start the application
python3 main.py

# Run in background
python3 main.py &
```

### Development Scripts (scripts/)
| Script | Purpose | Usage |
|--------|---------|-------|
| `test_login.py` | Test OAuth login flow | `python3 scripts/test_login.py` |
| `test_api.py` | Test API endpoints | `python3 scripts/test_api.py` |
| `test_curl_cffi.py` | Test Cloudflare bypass | `python3 scripts/test_curl_cffi.py` |
| `debug_api.py` | Debug API responses | `python3 scripts/debug_api.py` |
